channel.title: Auxylate – by Tazmanian Ninja [TECH HOUSE]
channel.description:
Auxylate is a tech house I made, 100% in Auxy – despite having Bitwig, hardware synths and some great VSTs. I frickin' love making music in Auxy. It inspires me, and I whip up melodies and grooves faster than in Bitwig with it. And its sounds are great!
I wrote a post about the track, on my new (still work-in-progress) website: [https://tazmanian.ninja/auxylate](https://tazmanian.ninja/auxylate/)
Without further ado, here's the SoundCloud link: [https://soundcloud.com/tazmanian_ninja/sets/auxylate](https://soundcloud.com/tazmanian_ninja/sets/auxylate)
And here's the Spotify link: https://open.spotify.com/album/7MWPZskQyoHLbOl7OGXIah?si=SChKDkSpTWaRByR22uCeFQ
Please feel free to FOLLOW me, and add it to your playlists. I'm a better musician than promoter, so can need all the help and support you can muster up :smiley:
Links to other streaming services are in the post above!
Whaddya fink? Hot? Not? Maybe? :D
